.TH "gelic_card_reset_chain" 9 "gelic_card_reset_chain" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
gelic_card_reset_chain \- reset status of a descriptor chain
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" gelic_card_reset_chain
.BI "(struct gelic_card *card "  ","
.BI "struct gelic_descr_chain *chain "  ","
.BI "struct gelic_descr *start_descr "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "card" 12
card structure
.IP "chain" 12
address of chain
.IP "start_descr" 12
address of descriptor array
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Reset the status of dma descriptors to ready state
and re-initialize the hardware chain for later use
